{"tid":381993,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"［DIY撚］自製MP3機","createTime":"2017-08-31T11:16:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-05T15:53:57.000Z","uid":26449,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f5ecbdfea4885bfc61e98ee71c7e9b2aaf89bfd1","tid":381993,"uid":26449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T11:16:56.000Z","msg":"DIY MP3 PLAYER<br />\n<br />\n是咁的，小弟有一鋪DIY癮，每次有野想買都會諗下可唔可以自己整，上網爬下文研究下一步一步解決問題真係好好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n搵材料過程中你會發現，出面買既成品大部份價值都係個牌子。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/190418_70810b992cb44e6e85b11051508ce146.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F190418_70810b992cb44e6e85b11051508ce146.jpg&h=fa9e681b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n材料：<br />\nMP3模塊 $35<br />\n1500mAh鋰電池 $12<br />\n訂做亞加力膠板 $10<br />\n螺絲 $0<br />\n<br />\n塊板搭載左充電功，可以慳返唔少功夫。<br />\n可插卡、USB、藍牙接收、FM功能，35蚊黎講有咁既功能算好好<br />\n<br />\n1500mAh鋰電，平靚正！暫時無工具測試佢。<br />\n<br />\n亞加力膠板用電腦畫完圖就淘寶搵廠做激光切割，質素一般但可以接受<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/190549_32eb60abfc02bc8f0f8285fa67ae67db.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F190549_32eb60abfc02bc8f0f8285fa67ae67db.jpg&h=2aba3e4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去片（唔識貼youtube)<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/B1UVW9oqURg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FB1UVW9oqURg&d=xkDhTH0%2BgIIGeBhui0X5BWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=44d6cd1a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/B1UVW9oqURg</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/190500_44d21282c6cce886acdd56865a29b2fc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F190500_44d21282c6cce886acdd56865a29b2fc.jpg&h=1cb553f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本人木耳，唔識點講音質，但覺得同iphone 差唔到，幾好，9.5分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n準備下次做無線藍牙喇嘛，仲欠材料，下次再分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/191119_44372d5ef62c71f6a65ddf0370165e49.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F191119_44372d5ef62c71f6a65ddf0370165e49.jpg&h=d87b0ef8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aa5e3917646f6af92dc01bd66fb224ec966d5ab","tid":381993,"uid":67118,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T11:22:19.000Z","msg":"唔會入塵咩  四邊都無封口<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ea97ac19b76e7f512d56a16360af8043a44936d","tid":381993,"uid":26449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T11:27:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔會入塵咩  四邊都無封口<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n研究緊個3D打印，到時先解決到呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"470fac5b5691be450d07e41ee35c3e4fc56eabc6","tid":381993,"uid":88495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T13:01:39.000Z","msg":"插sd卡之後點控制入面d file,例如揀歌"},{"pid":"1811bf68c4c278f75bf0e72b1afeadeb1645349d","tid":381993,"uid":15823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T13:10:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔會入塵咩  四邊都無封口<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n研究緊個3D打印，到時先解決到呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家就咁都幾大舊下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw, 片頭210